      </ul>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>
        Questions, tips, or something I got wrong? The <a href="/contact/">contact</a> page is the place. I take mistakes seriously — there's an <a href="/editorial-standards/">editorial standards</a> page and a <a href="/corrections/">corrections policy</a> to hold me to.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>
  <SiteFooter />
</Base>
